{1: '1', 2: 'Bianca', 3: "Please don't stand on my ray, I won't be responsible for any accidental injuries.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "This is the battlefield. I won't be hiding behind my teammates like the Purifying Force.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Though the battle is over, the tension in the air is somehow getting higher...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: '???', 3: "It's probably not a bad thing. After all, emotions are subtle, and often have multiple forms.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: "Ah, I forgot to introduce myself. I'm Guinevere. Those rude guests woke me up.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: '...Already corrupted?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Guinevere', 3: 'Who knows? Changes always take place in silence, just like the emergence of emotions.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee, please test her immediately.', 3: '24', 4: 'Is that so?', 5: '24'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: "Well, that's a lie. A knock on the door was just the beginning, they hadn't had a chance to touch me yet.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Test her as usual.', 3: '28', 4: "It's a routine.", 5: '28'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: "I see. I'll check her integrity now.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Guinevere', 3: "So I'm guessing you're their king, right?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Not the king...', 3: '32', 4: "I'm their commandant.", 5: '32'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: "So you deny it? You're cute. I'm the one who could see the threads of fate.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: 'The threads of fate and those of emotions firmly linked to each other are intertwined in you.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: '... which makes you a beloved king.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: 'I guess you also love your people, right, my king?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: "Your frankness seems familiar to me. Perhaps I'm in love with you as well.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "...Aren't you, Commandant?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Guinevere', 3: "Don't be shy about admitting love, my king. Or should I say, the not-so-frank commandant?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: "But perhaps I'm in love with you after all.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Guinevere', 3: 'Sure it is.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: "Whether it's love or the emotions that include it, are all complicated and contradictory.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Guinevere', 3: 'Like the two over there...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Are you talking about Watanabe and Bianca?', 4: '1'}
{2: "Aren't those two done fighting?", 3: '52', 4: 'I guess so.', 5: '52'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Guinevere', 3: 'Are they enemies or friends? Allies for a moment or enemies for life?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'I guess I understand.', 3: '61', 4: "I don't understand.", 5: '61'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "I-I don't quite understand. But if what Miss Guinevere said is true, the commandant also loves...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "...Anyway, the integrity test has passed. I'll recycle the memory now.", 4: '1'}
